===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab|ふくろ|yomi=k|alt=嚢}}
From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=ふくろ}}. First attested in the ''{{w|Kojiki}}'' of 712 {{CE}}.<ref name="KDJ2">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten 2|袋・嚢}}</ref> From {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*pukoro|sort=ふくろ}}.

Very likely related to {{m|ja|含む|tr=fukumu|t=to include}},<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> also among others deriving from a root ''*puk-'' (e.g. {{m|ja|膨れる|tr=fukureru|t=to swell}}).

